# ─── Required ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Your SimpleMDM API key. Use a read-only key unless you explicitly need writes.
SIMPLEMDM_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# ─── Write actions (off by default) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Set to true only when you need lock/sync/restart/assign/script actions.
# Use a key scoped to the minimum required permissions before enabling this.
# SIMPLEMDM_ALLOW_WRITES=true

# ─── Future options (not yet supported on the companion app side) ───────────
# Placeholder: integration with Report-SimpleMDM (local app mode) and a
# SimpleMDM-MunkiReport enrichment module is scaffolded in the server code
# but is NOT yet supported by those companion apps. Do not enable these —
# they are listed here only as a pointer for future work. See src/index.ts
# and src/localAppClient.ts for the env var names when/if support lands.
